{"tid":1840190,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"政府唔理你既生死，但要求你為佢地賣命？","createTime":"2020-01-24T17:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T10:26:04.000Z","uid":254123,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0c9b2b11597fb39006c958d45958360c50db69cf","tid":1840190,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:55:48.000Z","msg":"To 前線醫護<br />\n<br />\n你可以繼續你既大愛，<br />\n<br />\n或者你有事後世會有人紀念你。<br />\n<br />\n但啲狗官既不作為，要你地用條命去幫佢地埋單，<br />\n<br />\n咁邊個為你地父母，屋企人埋單？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工只係需要你自己行出第一步就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n決定權係你手上面，同前途道德無關，你仲活著先有選擇權。"},{"pid":"f8c25d13fa5a0a6c745ff8ed6ca7ea7c6429f94f","tid":1840190,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b1e9f472beaa5e7604634e1bc9cefc8081cc00","tid":1840190,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"69a744552b43aefd00b87649b20a012952cfa536","tid":1840190,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:08:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6beb22000c3d0faa6eb12e63b314d6d98b81d2a2","tid":1840190,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/X2h3F7C.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"07480a07ed45276a11a4430898a772c82c0c829